title: Ep. - 251 - NIK SCALZO FROM QB1: BEYOND THE LIGHTS DINA RUIZ EASTWOOD REVIEWS REAL HOUSEWIVES OF BEVERLY HILLS
description:
Nik Scalzo appears in season 3 of QB1: Beyond the Lights, a documentary series which focuses on three high school quarterbacks from different backgrounds as they play their final season before moving on to NCAA Division I college football.

 

Dina Ruiz Eastwood is a famous Hollwood ex-wife, so Kate had her review Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.
